data.meta_description: Buy or sell your property with Heather Cooper at RE/MAX Prime Properties. Your RE/MAX agent in Markham is a trained professional with deep knowledge of the real estate market. RE/MAX is Canada's #1 Real Estate Brand. Visit this page to contact Heather Cooper.
data.text:
About Me

An experienced real estate veteran, Heather Cooper brings a wealth of knowledge from the resale, pre-construction and investment segments of the industry. Heather has worked at a boutique brokerage in the city, as well as a large suburban firm prior to finding her niche at RE/MAX Prime Properties. She has earned several sales achievement awards as well as being the recipient of the Community Ambassador Award in back to back years. As a team member on one of Canadaâ€™s top Real Estate teams, Heather continues to grow her career while mentoring new agents that enter the industry. Heather has assisted new agents launch their new career by providing them with a solid foundation for success. Her passion for Pre-Construction has allowed her to form strategic partnerships with builders and developers around the GTA and provides her clients with preferred pricing and terms which in turn allows them to maximize their return on investment.
